net.alantea.proper

Annotation Type Require


  • @Repeatable(value=Requires.class)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Inherited
public @interface Require
    The annotation Require, usable only on class definition. It is use to create or update if needed a property in the container during instance association with a container, with a content class type and optionnaly an action to trigger on each property value modification. It is possible to set multiple @Require annotations on the same class. This annotation is automatically inherited by derived classes.
